  "instructions": [
    "Bring a large pot of water to a boil and cook the noodles according to the package instructions.",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together the soy sauce, oyster sauce, and sesame oil.",
    "In a large skillet or wok, heat the vegetable oil over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the pork to the skillet and cook until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the ginger and garlic to the skillet and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Pour the soy sauce mixture into the skillet and stir to combine.",
    "Add the cooked noodles to the skillet and stir to combine with the pork and sauce.",
    "Season with salt to taste.",
    "Garnish with chopped scallions and serve immediately."
